{
  "stem": "27335.7",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then it was converted into a prisoner's-- no, not a prisoner's camp, but a-- an escape is what-- the Polish army, when Hitler invaded Poland, some-- some 120,000 of the Polish Army's officers escaped, and Hungary took them in because there's the ancient centuries of relationships between Hungary-- Hungary, who had-- and they put them into this-- into this summer resort camp.",
      "word_count": 63
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And but then-- then they let them-- they dispersed them in-- in the country and in Budapest.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But they still had an office there, where they picked up.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They-- they-- they-- relief, really a few-- few [NON-ENGLISH] there and so on.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was the-- he was the chief interrogator.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Rose.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The very next day, very next day when I was put into-- into cell four, in that prison, that Budapest one, they-- the prisoners-- the-- the prisoners-- no, the guards.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The-- the guards, the NCO's, the Non-Commissioned Officer, when I was let out to the-- to the toilet, he-- he told me.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There were good guys.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He told me, watch out this wild beast.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "His name was Rose.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Rose, a rose.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But there, in the prison, I-- I know that-- that he was-- he was known under the name of Rose.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it could've been his real name.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because was in the counter intelligence, you see.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I don't-- I don't recall, unless-- unless you misunderstood me on-- on--",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--on something.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because I'm-- I'm-- I know I'm going too fast, I think.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But where I was interrogated was several-- several people in Miskolc.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And here.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there were some who just-- we just went and went over and over where I was born.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I had to give-- I had to give the exact location.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
